Good morning,

Thanks
for reading The Backstory, your weekend review of the best new work emanati=
ng from Puck. Our hearts remain with the Los Angeles communities impacted b=
y last week=E2=80=99s fires, which are still burning but seem to finally be=
 under control. We encourage all Puck subscribers to support the worthy gro=
ups, like this one ( https://supportlafd.kindful.com/?campaign=3D1040812&fb=
clid=3DPAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaYCsJMFXSed_-UIi4B8i6-ABSydTzEOjibVqhNddz4ZKdoLY8=
